flowchart TD
    A[User opens recommendations] --> B[Frontend calls Recommendation Gateway]
    B --> C[Gateway collects user and trip context]
    C --> D[Call ML service with 3s timeout]
    D --> E{ML response valid?}
    E -->|Yes, confidence >= threshold| F[Return ML recommendations]
    E -->|No, unavailable| G[Use fallback engine]
    E -->|No, timeout > 3s| G
    E -->|No, low confidence| H{Partial good results?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Use hybrid mode]
    H -->|No| G
    G --> J[Rank candidates from internal data]
    I --> K[Merge strong ML + fallback candidates]
    J --> L[Unified API response]
    K --> L
    F --> L
    L --> M[Frontend renders recommendations]
    L --> N[Log mode, reason, timing, metrics]
